snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Private Idol Disc Vol 03 - Oshima Akemi (1996)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Private Idol Disc Vol. 3: Oshima Akemi is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Sada Soft, which was released in Japan in 1996.
